Q2 read student.dat and show percentage
student.dat example:
1 Amit 70 80 75 90
2 Neha 60 65 70 75

```php
<?php
$f = fopen("student.dat","r");
echo "<table border=1><tr><th>Roll</th><th>Name</th><th>OS</th><th>WT</th><th>DS</th><th>Python</th><th>%</th></tr>";
