Q2 route details by source
```php
<?php
$conn = pg_connect("host=localhost dbname=test user=postgres password=postgres");
$s = $_POST['source'] ?? '';
?>
<form method="post">
Source: <input type="text" name="source">
<input type="submit" value="Show">
